Toolchain to backup short messages.

1. SmsBackup. Android app to email the archive of messages to input address. Need Android 2.1 or later.
2. SmsHtmlPrinter. Desktop application to generate readable HTML file containing the messages. Run with the message archives generated by SmsBackup in the same folder. Need Java 1.6 or later.

Avaiable here: https://github.com/simonvy/MessageBackup/downloads